title: Ronnie James Dio - This Is Your Life [320k MP3]
description:
Ronnie James Dio This Is Your Life is a 2014 tribute album to singer-songwriter Ronnie James Dio, lead singer of several heavy metal bands including Elf, Rainbow, Black Sabbath, Heaven & Hell, and his own band Dio. The album features many of Dio's contemporaries performing songs originally recorded by Dio.

Dio died in 2010 from stomach cancer.
